Grammar

    0 $accept: function $end

    1 function: function_header variables body

    2 function_header: FUNCTION IDENTIFIER optional_parameters RETURNS type ';'
    3                | FUNCTION IDENTIFIER error ';'

    4 optional_parameters: parameters
    5                    | %empty

    6 parameters: parameters ',' parameter
    7           | parameter

    8 parameter: IDENTIFIER ':' type

    9 variables: variables variable
   10          | %empty

   11 variable: IDENTIFIER ':' type IS statement_
   12         | IDENTIFIER ':' LIST OF type IS list ';'
   13         | IDENTIFIER error IS statement_

   14 type: INTEGER
   15     | REAL
   16     | CHARACTER

   17 list: '(' expressions ')'

   18 expressions: expressions ',' expression
   19            | expression

   20 body: BEGIN_ statement_ END ';'

   21 statement_: statement ';'
   22           | error ';'

   23 statement: expression
   24          | WHEN condition ',' expression ':' expression
   25          | WHEN error ',' expression ':' expression
   26          | WHEN condition ',' error ':' expression
   27          | WHEN condition ',' expression ':' error
   28          | WHEN condition error expression ':' expression
   29          | WHEN condition ',' expression error
   30          | WHEN error
   31          | SWITCH expression IS cases OTHERS ARROW statement_ ENDSWITCH
   32          | IF condition THEN statement_ elsif_clauses ELSE statement_ ENDIF
   33          | FOLD direction operator list_choice ENDFOLD

   34 elsif_clauses: elsif_clauses ELSIF condition THEN statement_
   35              | %empty

   36 cases: cases case
   37      | %empty

   38 case: CASE INT_LITERAL ARROW statement_
   39     | CASE error ARROW statement_

   40 direction: LEFT
   41          | RIGHT

   42 operator: ADDOP
   43         | MULOP

   44 list_choice: list
   45            | IDENTIFIER

   46 condition: or_condition

   47 or_condition: or_condition OROP and_condition
   48             | and_condition

   49 and_condition: and_condition ANDOP not_condition
   50              | not_condition

   51 not_condition: NOTOP not_condition
   52              | relation

   53 relation: '(' condition ')'
   54         | expression RELOP expression

   55 expression: expression ADDOP term
   56           | term

   57 term: term MULOP power
   58     | term MODOP power
   59     | power

   60 power: unary EXPOP power
   61      | unary

   62 unary: NEGOP unary
   63      | primary

   64 primary: '(' expression ')'
   65        | INT_LITERAL
   66        | REAL_LITERAL
   67        | CHAR_LITERAL
   68        | IDENTIFIER '(' expression ')'
   69        | IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '(' (40) 17 53 64 68
    ')' (41) 17 53 64 68
    ',' (44) 6 18 24 25 26 27 29
    ':' (58) 8 11 12 24 25 26 27 28
    ';' (59) 2 3 12 20 21 22
